OL,3,CMan charged in connection with Martin
OL,4,CO'Hagan's murder
OL,6,FA man has been charged with fraud by
OL,7,Ffalse representation by detectives
OL,8,Finvestigating the murder of journalist
OL,9,FMartin O'Hagan almost 24 years ago.
OL,11,FThe man, aged 42 was arrested in
OL,12,FSheffield before being brought to
OL,13,FBelfast for questioning.
OL,15,FA property was also searched as part
OL,16,Fof the operation.
OL,18,FHe is due to appear before Craigavon
OL,19,FMagistrates' Court on May 2.
