OL,6,FMr O'Hagan, 51, was shot dead by
OL,7,Floyalist paramilitaries as he walked
OL,8,Fhome from a night out with his wife in
OL,9,FLurgan in September 2001.
OL,11,FThe LVF (Loyalist Volunteer Force)
OL,12,Fcarried out the attack.
OL,14,FNo-one has ever been successfully
OL,15,Fprosecuted for his murder.
