OL,3,CMan charged in connection with Martin
OL,4,CO'Hagan's murder
OL,6,FPatrick Corrigan, Amnesty
OL,7,FInternational's Northern Ireland
OL,8,FDirector, said the arrest was
OL,9,F"potentially the most significant
OL,10,Fdevelopment since charges against four
OL,11,Fmen were dropped in July 2010".
OL,13,F"The public execution of Martin
OL,14,FO'Hagan was designed to send a clear
OL,15,Fmessage to journalists in Northern
OL,16,FIreland that they are not safe," he
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,F"It is unacceptable that, in the 24
OL,20,Fyears since Martin O'Hagan was shot
OL,21,Fdead, no one has been held accountable.
