OL,6,F"This failure has created an
OL,7,Fenvironment of impunity for those who
OL,8,Fcontinue to threaten journalists in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland today."
OL,11,FA PSNI spokesperson added: "Detectives
OL,12,Ffrom Police Service of Northern
OL,13,FIreland's Legacy Investigation Branch,
OL,14,Finvestigating the murder of journalist
OL,15,FMartin O'Hagan in Lurgan in 2001, have
OL,16,Farrested a 42-year-old man as part of
OL,17,Fthe overall investigation.
